  "body": "[comment]: # (Please replace ... with your information. Remove < and >)\r\n\r\n### User Story\r\n\r\nAs a iPhone X user, I want to use Status so that it is optimized for my device.\r\n\r\n### Description\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Feature or Bug? i.e Type: Bug)\r\n*Type*: Bug\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (Describe the feature you would like, or briefly summarise the bug and what you did, what you expected to happen, and what actually happens. Sections below)\r\n*Summary*: There are black bars shown at the top and bottom of an iPhone X screen. As a user, this is jarring and detracts from the user experience. Instead, the app should take up the entire screen and be optimized for the safe areas and notch.\r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what you expected to happen.)\r\nExpected behavior is for the app to fill the black bars, respect safe areas, have the status bar display correctly, and cater to the notch.\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\n[comment]: # (Describe what actually happened.)\r\nSee the black bars in the screenshot.\r\n\r\n![img_0018 2](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/116099/33998901-f44b281c-e0b6-11e7-9ad4-c130372626db.jpg)\r\n\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n[comment]: # (Describe how we can replicate the bug step by step.)\r\nOpen Status on an iPhone X.\r\n\r\n\r\n### Solution\r\n[comment]: # (Please summarise the solution and provide a task list on what needs to be fixed.)\r\n*Summary*:  Apple has a full list of [required updates](https://developer.apple.com/ios/update-apps-for-iphone-x/).\r\n\r\nAlso possibly relevant, React Native introduced a [new API in 0.50.1](https://medium.com/react-native-training/react-native-iphonex-92ff511282af) for easily dealing with the safe area of an iPhone X. More [info here](https://blog.callstack.io/react-native-meets-iphonex-a0f5034f7a41).\r\n\r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n[comment]: # (Please do your best to fill this out.)\r\n* Status version: 0.9.12\r\n* Operating System:iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\n[comment]: # (if on Android please replicate bug whilst running adb logcat)\r\n```\r\n...\r\n```",
